mortemart...

01:01:13.804 --> 01:01:16.338
Whom he introduced."

01:01:31.855 --> 01:01:33.321
Oh, hi.

01:01:33.323 --> 01:01:37.025
You are heather, aren't you?
Please come in.

01:01:37.027 --> 01:01:41.329
Charlie brown told me
he had invited you to the party.

01:01:41.331 --> 01:01:44.499
I don't know where charlie brown
is right now.

01:01:44.501 --> 01:01:47.035
But would you like to dance?

01:01:53.010 --> 01:01:56.344
Chuck, where are you?

01:01:56.346 --> 01:02:00.215
It's just a few seconds before
midnight.

01:02:00.217 --> 01:02:02.451
Chuck, chuck.

01:02:46.196 --> 01:02:49.297
Chuck, how could you do this to
me?

01:02:49.299 --> 01:02:54.770
When midnight came along,
I was the only one standing all
alone.

01:02:54.772 --> 01:02:56.271
I, uh... I...

01:02:56.273 --> 01:03:01.543
Big brother, my sweet baboo
didn't dance with me at
midnight.

01:03:01.545 --> 01:03:03.245
And do you know why?

01:03:03.247 --> 01:03:04.946
Well, uh, I, uh....

01:03:04.948 --> 01:03:09.151
Because he danced with your
friend, the little red-haired
girl.

01:03:09.153 --> 01:03:11.953
He did what?

01:03:11.955 --> 01:03:15.957
Gee, charlie brown,
I didn't know where you went.

01:03:15.959 --> 01:03:20.295
But, wow, your friend is sure a
good dancer.

01:03:20.297 --> 01:03:23.064
You mean she was here?

01:03:23.066 --> 01:03:28.970
The little red-haired girl was
here and I missed her?

01:03:41.485 --> 01:03:44.252
Happy new year, charles.

01:03:53.197 --> 01:03:57.699
Hurry up, charlie brown.
We'll be late for school.

01:04:00.337 --> 01:04:04.172
Did you finish war and peace,
charlie brown?

01:04:04.174 --> 01:04:07.509
I finished at 3:00 this morning.

01:04:07.511 --> 01:04:10.212
How did you like it, charlie
brown?

01:04:10.214 --> 01:04:13.415
I don't remember a thing.

01:04:14.618 --> 01:04:18.220
- Did you turn in your report?
- Yes.

01:04:18.222 --> 01:04:20.956
What did the teacher say about
it?

01:04:20.958 --> 01:04:22.824
What grade did you get?

01:04:22.826 --> 01:04:24.359
A d-minus.

01:04:24.361 --> 01:04:27.629
The lowest grade without
failing.

01:04:27.631 --> 01:04:30.799
Gee, I'm sorry, charlie brown.

01:04:30.801 --> 01:04:33.201
The teacher said it looked like
the sort of report...

01:04:33.203 --> 01:04:38.974
That was written after
midnight on the last day of
christmas vacation.

01:04:38.976 --> 01:04:40.575
What did you say?

01:04:40.577 --> 01:04:42.577
What could I say?

01:04:42.579 --> 01:04:47.749
I congratulated her
on her remarkable insight.

01:04:48.719 --> 01:04:51.486
Did you see what our next
assignment is?

01:04:51.488 --> 01:04:53.555
No. What is it?

01:04:53.557 --> 01:04:59.227
To read crime and punishment
by dostoevsky.

01:04:59.229 --> 01:05:02.797
Happy new year, charlie brown.
